     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
 
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
      ** Inputs
      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
      ** Other parms
      ** Field(s) requiring validation
     C                   PARM                    DDTRAS
      ** OUTPUTS
      ** Error fields/message IDs/message data (arrays) from/to caller
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXAr
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXAr
      ** Trust Agreement Status - OK
     C                   PARM                    DDTRASOK
 
